00:00:01.960 --> 00:00:07.800
We are living in these modern times

00:00:07.865 --> 00:00:10.785
which are very eventful

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:22.113
In last 50 or 60 years so many things have happened

00:00:27.286 --> 00:00:35.326
and the churning should bring forth many truths before us

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:52.912
First we have to realize that man has separated from each other.

00:00:59.547 --> 00:01:02.667
The relationships that existed once upon a time

00:01:03.789 --> 00:01:06.549
are no more to be found today.

00:01:12.993 --> 00:01:20.553
And on the collective level we are waiting for a shock.

00:01:25.939 --> 00:01:30.939
God knows what sort of a disaster is going to fall upon us.

00:01:35.735 --> 00:01:41.735
Loudly. God knows what sort of a disaster is going to fall.

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:43.520
You can come here, better.

00:01:53.620 --> 00:01:57.500
And in these uncertain times only

00:01:59.949 --> 00:02:06.069
we have to realize that there must some way out.

00:02:16.279 --> 00:02:21.479
The way we understand through our mental projections,

00:02:27.573 --> 00:02:31.653
the solution is not in the view.

00:02:35.554 --> 00:02:41.914
The solution that we think is the solution becomes a bondage, a system.

00:02:48.006 --> 00:02:54.486
We try to break one system and build up another one

00:02:54.735 --> 00:02:58.415
and that's how we find ourselves

00:02:58.440 --> 00:03:01.520
miserably caught up into these systems.

00:03:10.434 --> 00:03:17.034
So there has gone something wrong in our understanding of the problem.

00:03:21.215 --> 00:03:24.255
We have to little bit stand back

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:28.425
and see what mistake we must have committed.

00:03:35.695 --> 00:03:40.935
Once upon a time I came to Belgium on a ship,

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:44.120
it was a very thriving shipping company.

00:03:52.600 --> 00:03:56.760
All that is showing us

00:03:56.960 --> 00:04:03.240
that even our economic enterprises come to a halt.

00:04:13.835 --> 00:04:23.966
Now other enterprises on the emotional basis

00:04:26.448 --> 00:04:35.248
or on the physical basis are giving us a feeling of confusion.

00:04:41.720 --> 00:04:45.560
Like today only a gentleman told me

00:04:45.830 --> 00:04:49.476
that allopathic medicines are rather dangerous.

00:04:56.527 --> 00:04:59.647
So I said: "What is the solution you have for it?"

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:05.640
The reason the cement is very dangerous

00:05:05.960 --> 00:05:09.840
because it retains lot of moisture.

00:05:16.380 --> 00:05:19.620
Then he said that the plastic is very dangerous ...

00:05:23.935 --> 00:05:29.415
Ultimately it looked as if everything that we eat or live into

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:31.360
seems to be a dangerous spot.

00:05:41.525 --> 00:05:48.165
Now we should understand that the progress that we have made so far

00:05:48.682 --> 00:05:51.282
is recoiling back upon ourselves.

00:06:00.390 --> 00:06:03.150
As if the progress was linear.

00:06:06.321 --> 00:06:10.561
I went to Houston 10 years back nobody would look at you.

00:06:11.880 --> 00:06:15.800
Nobody would look at you, there were so rich you see.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.080
Dynasty and all that, in Houston.

00:06:23.080 --> 00:06:29.842
And today they told me if anybody is willing to pay even the amount

00:06:29.867 --> 00:06:34.200
we have to pay to the bank we are willing to sell our houses.

00:06:43.740 --> 00:06:50.060
This ask for oil, oil, oil, oil, now they don't want oil.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:07:01.880
Then in the science we discovered atomic bomb, hydrogen bomb,

00:07:02.080 --> 00:07:03.880
all kinds of things.

00:07:09.647 --> 00:07:14.487
Then we have discovered our computers.

00:07:18.537 --> 00:07:22.297
And now we are worried that this computer will take over us.

00:07:29.114 --> 00:07:31.594
Everything is getting out of control.

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:36.080
Where does the control lie?

00:07:40.567 --> 00:07:47.687
We talk of peace but how will you establish it?

00:07:49.851 --> 00:07:52.851
There is a control within us.

00:07:57.183 --> 00:08:00.183
We can control everything.

00:08:03.620 --> 00:08:07.420
First we have to be in control with ourselves.

00:08:11.066 --> 00:08:14.026
First we have to know ourselves.

00:08:16.294 --> 00:08:21.494
And this feeling is very fashionable I should say.

00:08:26.340 --> 00:08:29.144
So many people are seeking the truth.

00:08:32.568 --> 00:08:37.328
Is a special quality of human beings who are seekers.

00:08:41.445 --> 00:08:48.205
And when they try to seek the idea goes to the market as usual.

00:08:51.042 --> 00:08:53.402
It goes to the market, the idea.

00:08:56.043 --> 00:09:02.483
So the demand is there for somebody to guide you in your seeking.

00:09:05.687 --> 00:09:11.767
So you have people who provide a kind of a market.

00:09:15.647 --> 00:09:18.767
You get so many money spinning gurus,

00:09:21.776 --> 00:09:30.056
they talk to you about peace and happiness and emancipation.

00:09:34.834 --> 00:09:36.954
But you have to pay.

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:41.920
Today somebody told me in the car that the people who

00:09:42.120 --> 00:09:45.760
were telephoning asked how much do we have to pay.

00:09:55.146 --> 00:09:57.946
How much did you pay to Christ?

00:10:00.780 --> 00:10:05.220
How much are you going to pay for the love of God?

00:10:07.646 --> 00:10:12.886
Is nothing human that you can purchase it.

00:10:16.255 --> 00:10:19.295
The seekers if they realize one little point

00:10:19.320 --> 00:10:24.040
that you cannot pay for it, for your evolution you cannot pay.

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:29.360
That's one point, if you realize, half of the work is done.

00:10:41.655 --> 00:10:46.175
The second point is that it is your evolution

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:50.800
which is a living force, of living divine.

00:10:58.135 --> 00:11:03.055
This living force which has made you from amoeba stage

00:11:03.080 --> 00:11:06.960
to human being is going to make you something higher.

00:11:15.015 --> 00:11:18.735
The living force that has created these beautiful flowers,

00:11:18.760 --> 00:11:21.560
how much did these flowers pay to that?

00:11:27.448 --> 00:11:33.328
How much did they pay for it? Or how much did they exert for it?

00:11:36.405 --> 00:11:40.485
So this evolution has to be spontaneous.

00:11:43.243 --> 00:11:46.483
Effortless.

00:11:47.924 --> 00:11:50.844
And that is what is Sahaja.

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:56.320
'Saha' means 'with' and 'ja' means 'born with you'.

00:12:03.411 --> 00:12:07.051
It is born with you, the power.

00:12:09.976 --> 00:12:13.376
And 'yoga' means 'the union with the divine'.

00:12:16.135 --> 00:12:22.375
So every human being has a right to get to that state

00:12:22.400 --> 00:12:25.160
where you become one with the divine.

00:12:33.566 --> 00:12:39.246
We have heard about the all-pervading divine power.

00:12:43.975 --> 00:12:48.895
Right from Lao Tse to Christ to Buddha,

00:12:48.920 --> 00:12:51.760
all of them have talked about it.

00:12:57.301 --> 00:13:01.301
We did not know about the ether before.

00:13:06.497 --> 00:13:12.057
But we have heard about the Divine power, which is all-pervading.

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:23.360
Once you are united with it, connected with it,

00:13:24.478 --> 00:13:32.478
then only you realize that you are a part and parcel of the whole.

00:13:39.895 --> 00:13:45.175
But before that it's only talk, talk of religion,

00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:49.080
talk about all philosophies, it's just a talk.

00:13:55.780 --> 00:14:00.660
Without any experience of this Divine power,

00:14:00.975 --> 00:14:06.455
if we are going to believe into these talks and these dogmas

00:14:06.480 --> 00:14:09.680
also these mental projections

00:14:10.200 --> 00:14:14.760
we reach a state where we will say we don't believe in it.

00:14:25.603 --> 00:14:29.563
But this is not the way to know the Divine.

00:14:32.840 --> 00:14:37.720
In the Bible it is said that, "I will appear before you

00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:39.720
like tongues of flames."

00:14:45.215 --> 00:14:48.975
In the Koran it is said that at the time of resurrection

00:14:49.023 --> 00:14:51.224
your hands will speak.

00:14:56.375 --> 00:15:01.615
You'll be surprised in the Koran, more chapters are dedicated

00:15:01.640 --> 00:15:06.240
to the resurrection time than to the doomsday.

00:15:14.877 --> 00:15:21.037
They talk of the doomsday because that is how you frighten people.

00:15:25.418 --> 00:15:28.538
So this resurrection has to come first.

00:15:32.775 --> 00:15:37.775
Of course in all the Indian scriptures it is described

00:15:37.975 --> 00:15:44.215
that the only way to be in charge,

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:48.960
to be in control yourself is through Self-realization.

00:15:57.406 --> 00:16:00.166
We do not know ourselves.

00:16:02.452 --> 00:16:07.212
People get cancer, they don't know they have cancer.

00:16:11.508 --> 00:16:16.308
People get mad, schizophrenic, they don't know they are mad.

00:16:21.135 --> 00:16:23.775
They don't know because they don't know their body,

00:16:23.800 --> 00:16:25.520
they don't know themselves.

00:16:30.138 --> 00:16:34.258
So to find out about ourselves we have to go inside.

00:16:39.370 --> 00:16:42.370
By going outside you cannot find out.

00:16:45.218 --> 00:16:47.338
How do you go inside?

00:16:49.210 --> 00:16:51.970
You are all paying attention to me.

00:16:52.000 --> 00:16:57.240
But if I say please pay attention to yourself, you'll say, "How?".

00:17:02.604 --> 00:17:05.364
You cannot take your attention inside.

00:17:07.775 --> 00:17:11.575
But you must know: the One who has made us

00:17:11.600 --> 00:17:14.880
has put all that in image within us.

00:17:18.975 --> 00:17:21.575
As the one who has made this instrument

00:17:21.600 --> 00:17:24.040
has also left the connection there.

00:17:28.374 --> 00:17:31.974
So it has just to be plugged to the mains, that's all.

00:17:34.915 --> 00:17:37.195
Then it works, fantastically.

00:17:38.735 --> 00:17:42.095
Only we are not connected to mains, that's all.

00:17:42.120 --> 00:17:44.880
There's nothing else to be done.

00:17:48.895 --> 00:17:51.455
Once you are connected to the mains

00:17:51.855 --> 00:17:55.615
you'll get all your physical benefits,

00:17:55.640 --> 00:18:01.171
mental benefits, emotional benefits and spiritual benefits.

00:18:09.681 --> 00:18:12.650
I'll tell you about the spiritual.

00:18:16.197 --> 00:18:23.273
The spiritual benefit is that you get awakened to a new awareness.

00:18:28.471 --> 00:18:32.679
That on your central nervous system

00:18:32.720 --> 00:18:37.981
you can feel the collective consciousness.

00:18:43.873 --> 00:18:51.873
That you can feel yourself and you can feel others within yourself.

00:18:57.696 --> 00:19:01.149
We have a force within us

00:19:02.160 --> 00:19:06.024
which is the power of pure desire.

00:19:08.691 --> 00:19:11.880
Is not an impure desire.

