As you know in economics it is said that the power, the

00:19:20.320 --> 00:19:26.255
satisfaction out of anything passes on from one to another.

00:19:26.280 --> 00:19:30.624
Like I want to buy a house then I want to buy a car

00:19:30.649 --> 00:19:32.719
then I want to buy that, I am never satisfied.

00:19:32.744 --> 00:19:35.514
So in general it is never satiable.

00:19:47.135 --> 00:19:54.055
But the pure desire within us is the desire to be one with the divine

00:19:54.080 --> 00:19:58.239
so that we get into the eternal life.

00:20:06.720 --> 00:20:09.632
This desire has to be awakened.

00:20:13.176 --> 00:20:17.311
Once it is awakened in this human awareness

00:20:17.776 --> 00:20:21.696
you can feel on your central nervous system

00:20:28.040 --> 00:20:32.251
these centers that are within your body

00:20:35.768 --> 00:20:38.490
which are subtle centers

00:20:40.356 --> 00:20:48.971
and when they are in any way in trouble you get all these problems.

00:20:55.144 --> 00:20:59.701
You can feel them on your fingertips.

00:21:02.975 --> 00:21:06.615
It's something in English, to feel something on your fingertips,

00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:08.269
means it is very easy.

00:21:13.895 --> 00:21:16.575
So you feel it on your fingertips,

00:21:16.600 --> 00:21:19.920
your own centers which are in trouble.

00:21:24.387 --> 00:21:29.600
And you feel the centers of another person.

00:21:34.375 --> 00:21:38.895
