We are at a stage which I can describe you with an analogy.

00:22:23.719 --> 00:22:31.107
Like in the car you have got a brake and an accelerator.

00:22:34.575 --> 00:22:38.695
In that way in our body also there are two nadis, two systems,

00:22:38.720 --> 00:22:42.393
two channels, left and right which act

00:22:42.468 --> 00:22:45.880
as the brake and the accelerator.

00:22:52.306 --> 00:22:56.506
In the autonomous nervous system the left and the right sympathetic.

00:23:00.894 --> 00:23:05.039
The central part is for our evolution.

00:23:09.014 --> 00:23:15.135
So once we learn how to use the accelerator and also the brake

00:23:15.160 --> 00:23:20.465
we become a driver. That means we come in the center.

00:23:29.182 --> 00:23:33.815
That means we become evolved enough to be

00:23:33.840 --> 00:23:36.160
automatically driving the car.

00:23:42.013 --> 00:23:46.187
But then there is the master sitting behind.

00:23:51.040 --> 00:23:54.760
