00:23:58.530 --> 00:24:00.255
And you see the driver in you and

00:24:00.280 --> 00:24:06.008
you see the brake and the accelerator.

00:24:11.286 --> 00:24:13.790
And you are in charge.

00:24:16.314 --> 00:24:24.314
